    "## 2. 初始化组件"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "config = Config.from_yaml(\"../config.yaml\")\n",
    "\n",
    "llm_client = LLMClient(\n",
    "    endpoint=config.llm.cloud_endpoint,\n",
    "    timeout=config.llm.timeout\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "model_selector = ModelSelector(cloud_endpoint=config.llm.cloud_endpoint)\n",
    "compressor = LLMCompressor(llm_client, model_selector)\n",
    "reconstructor = LLMReconstructor(llm_client)\n",
    "evaluator = QualityEvaluator()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ 组件初始化成功\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 质量指标详解\n",
    "\n",
    "系统使用5个核心质量指标：\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **压缩比 (Compression Ratio)**: 原始大小 / 压缩后大小\n",
    "2. **语义相似度 (Semantic Similarity)**: 使用 embedding 计算余弦相似度\n",
    "3. **实体准确率 (Entity Accuracy)**: 关键实体的保留率\n",
    "4. **BLEU 分数**: 文本相似度评分\n",
    "5. **综合分数 (Overall Score)**: 加权平均分数"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 测试不同质量级别"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "test_text = \"\"\"\n",
    "On January 15, 2024, John Smith met with Mary Johnson at 123 Main Street.\n",
    "They discussed the Q4 budget of $1.2 million and agreed on marketing allocation\n",
    "of $400,000. The meeting lasted 2 hours and covered product roadmap for 2024.\n",
    "\"\"\".strip()\n",
    "\n",
    "quality_levels = [QualityLevel.LOW, QualityLevel.STANDARD, QualityLevel.HIGH]\n",
    "results = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "for quality_level in quality_levels:\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n测试质量级别: {quality_level.value}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 选择模型\n",
    "    model = model_selector.select_model(\n",
    "        memory_type=MemoryType.TEXT,\n",
    "        text_length=len(test_text),\n",
    "        quality_requirement=quality_level\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 压缩和重构\n",
    "    compressed = await compressor.compress(test_text, MemoryType.TEXT)\n",
    "    reconstructed = await reconstructor.reconstruct(compressed)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 评估质量\n",
    "    metrics = evaluator.evaluate(test_text, reconstructed.full_text, compressed)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    results[quality_level.value] = metrics\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"  压缩比: {metrics.compression_ratio:.2f}x\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  语义相似度: {metrics.semantic_similarity:.3f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  实体准确率: {metrics.entity_accuracy:.3f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  综合分数: {metrics.overall_score:.3f}\")"
   ]
